Formulation diversity is also a critical factor influencing the adoption of biofungicides for soil treatment. The availability of liquid, powder, and granular formulations gives farmers flexibility in choosing the most suitable product based on their cultivation practices, equipment, and soil conditions. Furthermore, advancements in formulation technologies are leading to improved efficacy, storage stability, and application convenience, driving the overall market growth.

